.cs 4 on
.item 'SHOW SHARE Command' 'Updated on 12/13/84 by AEH'
.boxon
SHOW SHARE filename
.*         <------>
.* FIELD COMMAND SHO SHAR filename
.boxoff

.* DESCRIPTION
The SHOW SHARE command displays the SHARE status set by the file owner
for the specified file.  If SET SHARE is set, ORVYL responds:

        filename attachable share only.

If SET NOSHARE is in effect, ORVYL responds:

        filename attachable normally.

See the SET SHARE command for information on setting share status.

.* SELECT 'SHOW SHARE Command Options'
.us Option Descriptions

.* OPTION filename
.optix filename
filename\\\\\\\\\\\the name of the ORVYL file whose SHARE status you
                   want to display.

.cs 4 off
